4. Syntax

Basic syntax:

<button onClick={handleClick}>
  Click Me
</button>

Function:

function handleClick() {
  alert("Button Clicked");
}


5. Line-by-Line Explanation

Code:

function App() {

  function handleClick() {
    alert("Button Clicked");
  }

  return (
    <button onClick={handleClick}>
      Click Me
    </button>
  );
}

Explanation:

function App()

Creates component.

function handleClick()

Function that runs when event occurs.


