Performance Tips
Avoid Inline Functions Excessively

Less preferred:

<button onClick={() => handleClick()}>

Preferred:

<button onClick={handleClick}>

Use inline functions only when passing parameters.

Keep Event Logic Small

Bad:

function handleClick() {
  // 200 lines
}

Better:

function handleClick() {
  updateUser();
}
